# EXISTING STRUCTURES

There are no existing structures to report as this is the first report.

# ERROR TIPS

### Errors when extracting from a furnace that does not contain the item
-  Ensure that the furnace contains the item you are trying to extract before attempting to extract it. The furnace at (4.0, -60.0) does not contain iron plates.
### Errors when inserting items into a furnace when inventory is full
- Ensure that the agent has enough space in its inventory to harvest coal.
- Ensure that the agent has enough space in its inventory to insert copper ore into the copper furnace.

# NAMESPACE

No functions have been defined by the agent.
